OL,6,FFinancial officials are investigating
OL,7,Fcar loans taken before January 28,
OL,8,F2021, when the law changed banning
OL,9,F"discretionary interest rate"
OL,10,Fcommissions.
OL,12,FIt's claimed that these allowed car
OL,13,Fdealers to add to a buyer's repayments
OL,14,Fto boost earnings via commissions.
OL,16,FOne car sales insider, who did not
OL,17,Fwant to be named, told ITV News the
OL,18,Fpractice of discretionary rates was
OL,19,F"widespread" with "kickbacks" for the
OL,20,Fcar dealer.
