OL,3,CITV News figures show 865,000 seek mis-
OL,4,Csold car finance claims
OL,6,FSome of these claims date back three
OL,7,Fyears and experts say there are many
OL,8,Fmore yet to be disclosed.
OL,10,FIt's free and relatively
OL,11,Fstraightforward to complain to your
OL,12,Fcar loan provider and the Financial
OL,13,FOmbudsman - we are providing some
OL,14,Fuseful links below.
OL,16,FA claims management company can take
OL,17,Faway some of the work, but they can
OL,18,Fcharge 15-20% of your compensation.
OL,19,FEven if you make a claim, firms don't
OL,20,Fneed to respond until 25th Sept at the
OL,21,Fearliest.
