OL,4,Csold car finance claims
OL,6,FConsumer expert Alex Neill shares her
OL,7,Ftop tips if you think you might be
OL,8,Feligible to claim
OL,10,FMy ITV colleague Martin Lewis is
OL,11,Frightly credited with directing public
OL,12,Fattention to loan compensation claims
OL,13,Fand believes millions could eventually
OL,14,Fbe due payouts on a scale in the same
OL,15,Fleague as PPI, which was worth just
OL,16,Funder #40 billion.
OL,18,FThere are potential bumps in the road
OL,19,Fahead, with fears that the sheer
OL,20,Fnumber of claims will swamp financial
OL,21,Ffirms.
