OL,6,FThat's why it's vital that officials
OL,7,Festablish a fair and consistent way
OL,8,Ffor any payouts to work.
OL,10,FAnother big danger is that these
OL,11,Fclaims are not covered by the
OL,12,FFinancial Services Compensation
OL,13,FScheme, so if your loan provider goes
OL,14,Fout of business - you may not get what
OL,15,Fyou are owed.
OL,17,FPerhaps the biggest hurdle will be the
OL,18,Fresponse from loan firms, who so far
OL,19,Fhave denied that customers were
OL,20,Ftreated unfairly.
